\c 2
\nb
\v 1 Asi ndakazvipira izvi mumoyo mangu, kuti handidi kuuyazve kwamuri nokushungurudzika.
\v 2 Nokuti kana ndichikushungurudzai, ndianiko uchandifadza, kunze kwaiye wakashungurudzwa neni?
\v 3 Zvino ndakakunyorerai chinhu ichochi \add kuti\add* zvimwe kana ndasvika, ndirege kushungurudzwa naivo vanofanira kundifadza; nechivimbo mamuri mose, kuti kufara kwangu ndokwenyu mose.
\v 4 Nokuti mukutambudzika kukuru nokushungurudzika komoyo ndakakunyorerai nemisodzi mizhinji, kwete kuti muchemedzwe, asi kuti muzive rudo rukuru rwandinokudai narwo.
\v 5 Zvino kana mumwe akashungurudza, haana kushungurudza ini, asi muchidimbu (kuti ndirege kukuremedzai) mose.
\v 6 Kuranga uku kwakakwanira wakadai ndiko kwavazhinji.
\v 7 Kuti panzvimbo yaizvozvi zviri nani kuti mumukangamwire nokunyaradza, kuti wakadaro arege kuvodzwa moyo kwazvo neshungu huru.
\v 8 Naizvozvo ndinokunyengetedzai kuti musimbise rudo kwaari.
\v 9 Nokuti ndakanyorerawo izvi kuti ndizive uchapupu hwenyu kana muchiteerera pazvinhu zvose.
\v 10 Zvino iye wamunokangamwira chinhu, neni \add ndinomukangamwira\add*wo; nokuti ini kana ndichikangamwira chinhu, uyo wandinenge ndakakangamwira, ndinozviita nokuda kwenyu pamberi paKristu;
\v 11 kuti tzvimwe Satani ungatora mukana wedu; nokuti hatizi vasingazivi mano ake.
\s Zvibereko zvakuparidza kwaPauro
\p
\v 12 Zvino, ndakati ndichisvika paTroasi \add ne\add*evhangeri yaKristu, ndichizarurirwa mukova munaKristu,
\v 13 handina kuwana zororo pamweya wangu, nokuti handina kuwanapo Tito hama yangu; asi ndakawonekana navo, ndikabvapo ndikaenda Makedhonia.
\v 14 Asi ngaavongwe Mwari, unotikundisa nguva dzose munaKristu, uye unoratidza nesu kose-kose hwema hwokuziva kwake.
\v 15 Nokuti isu tiri hwema hwunonhuwira hwaKristu kunaMwari, pana ivo vanoponeswa navanoparara.
\v 16 Kunavamwe hwema hworufu mukufa; nokuna vamwe hwema hwoupenyu muupenyu. Zvino ndianiko ungakwanisa zvinhu izvi?
\v 17 Nokuti hatifanani navazhinji vanokanganisa shoko raMwari; asi sevechokwadi, aye sezvinobva kunaMwari pachiso chaMwari tinotaura tiri munaKristu.
